data.name: sqlSelectCommand1.CommandText
data.value: select lend.cuname1,lend.lememo1,lend.lememo,lend.xa1no,lend.xa1name,lend.xa1par,lend.x3no,lend.rate,lend.emno,lend.emname,lend.leoverflag,lendd.* from lend left join lendd on lend.leno=lendd.leno where (leoverflag='0' or leoverflag is null) and lendd.cuno=(@cuno) order by lendd.ledate asc
